      <title>韩国核电站运营商因安全担忧屏蔽人工智能服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/korea-nuclear-plant-operator-blocks-ai-services-on-security-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国营核反应堆运营商韩国水电核电公司出于安全考虑，已在其系统中阻止使用所有人工智能服务，包括 DeepSeek 和 ChatGPT。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/korea-nuclear-plant-operator-blocks-ai-services-on-security-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 08:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股价下跌 50% 后，维斯塔斯计划回购 1 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vestas-to-return-profit-to-investors-with-stronger-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力发电系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 宣布回购 1 亿欧元（1.04 亿美元）的股票，并恢复向投资者派发股息，此前该公司因成本飙升导致巨额亏损，多年来一直努力提高价格，如今开始收获成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vestas-to-return-profit-to-investors-with-stronger-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国市场重新开放，铜价因贸易关系保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/copper-advances-on-weaker-dollar-as-chinese-markets-reopen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，伦敦铜价保持涨势，投资者正在权衡中美贸易战的影响。中国市场在农历新年假期后重新开市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/copper-advances-on-weaker-dollar-as-chinese-markets-reopen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人节日期间大肆消费，但消费焦虑依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-services-gauge-unexpectedly-slows-despite-holiday-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农历新年假期期间，中国消费者的旅游和观影支出创下了历史新高，但这一奢侈消费尚未带来消费经济的好转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-services-gauge-unexpectedly-slows-despite-holiday-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:52:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国 IPO 热潮降温，多年来表现最好的公司首日表现不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/lg-cns-set-to-debut-after-south-korea-s-biggest-ipo-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG CNS Co. 首次公开募股 (IPO) 规模为 1.2 万亿韩元（8.21 亿美元），在首尔交易日首日股价下跌，成为韩国两年多以来最大的新股上市交易。]]></description>
