      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税影响前景 美国债券交易员态度趋于中性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/traders-turn-more-neutral-on-us-bonds-as-tariffs-cloud-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关税边缘政策给经济和美联储的前景蒙上阴影，并有可能加剧市场动荡，债券交易员在过去一周退出了期货和现货美国国债的押注，转而采取更加中性的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/traders-turn-more-neutral-on-us-bonds-as-tariffs-cloud-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 21:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球汽车关税之痛从亚洲蔓延至美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/europe-s-car-shares-drop-as-vw-bmw-stellantis-face-tariff-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的新关税威胁到墨西哥和加拿大工厂的汽车销量，导致全球汽车股周一暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/europe-s-car-shares-drop-as-vw-bmw-stellantis-face-tariff-pain</guid>
